# ⚔️ AI vs Human - Rock Paper Scissors

A fun browser-based Rock-Paper-Scissors game where you play against an AI using **hand gestures** detected via your webcam.

---

## 🎮 How to Play

1. Open `index.html` in your browser (Chrome/Edge recommended).  
2. Allow camera access when prompted.  
3. Choose your **Battle Mode**: Best of 3 (currently fully supported).  
4. Show your gesture (Rock ✊, Paper ✋, or Scissors ✌️) in front of the camera.  
5. Click **Start Round** to play.  
6. Watch the AI move and check the results.  
7. First player to reach majority wins the game.

---

## 🖥️ Features

- Real-time hand gesture detection using **MediaPipe Hands**.  
- Animated AI move reveal.  
- Scoreboard and round tracking.  
- Modern glass-style UI with animated backgrounds.  

---

## 📂 Files

- `index.html` – main HTML file  
- `style.css` – styling and animations  
- `script.js` – game logic and gesture detection  

---

## ⚡ Notes

- Currently, **Best of 3** works perfectly.  
- Camera access is required to detect gestures.  
- Tested in modern browsers (Chrome, Edge).  

---

## 🚀 Deployment

You can deploy the game via [GitHub Pages](https://pages.github.com/) for free.  

1. Go to your repository → Settings → Pages → Source → main branch → `/root`  
2. Save and open the generated URL to play online.

---

Enjoy the game! 🎉
